al\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4720852-broadcom-custom-compute-chips-and-generative-ai-saas-demand-are-real\" target=\"_blank\">Broadcom </a>(NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVGO#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVGO#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" target=\"_blank\">AVGO</a>) in September 2024, discussing its robust growth prospects through custom silicon chips and higher networking demand, which supported the excellent top-line expansion, the high-margin subscriptions/ services</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183527075/image_2183527075.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4744965-broadcom-custom-compute-chips-remain-growth-tailwinds-buy-the-upcoming-correction", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 00:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745677", "title": "Barclays: Still Trading At 0.6x 2026 Book Value", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625756585/image_1625756585.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Barclays office building in New York, NY, USA on August 17, 2022.\" data-id=\"1625756585\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625756585/image_1625756585.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625756585/image_1625756585.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625756585/image_1625756585.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625756585/image_1625756585.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625756585/image_1625756585.jpg?io=ge